      "value": "<p>Through many battles you have learned to aim your strikes at vital points that would send your enemy reeling in pain.</p><p> Starting at 15th level, when you would hit a creature with a Cursed Blast or Cursed Strike you can spend 2 cursed energy to daze them on a successful hit.</p><p> When Magnified: If a creature is bleeding or cursed you can force them to make a Constitution saving throw or be stunned until the start of your next turn on a failed save.</p><p></p>",
